com.madrobot.graphics.bitmap

Class BlurFilters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.madrobot.graphics.bitmap.BlurFilters

  • public class BlurFilters
extends Object
    Collection of various blur filters

    Gaussian Blur
    Gaussian using the radius of 2

    Motion Blur
    Motion blur with angle 1.0f and distance 5.0f.

    Box Blur
    Box blur with hRadius and vRadius of 5.0f. with 1 iteration

    Maximum

    Minimum

    Median

    Author:
    elton.stephen.kent

      • boxBlur

        public static Bitmap boxBlur(Bitmap bitmap,
             float hRadius,
             float vRadius,
             int iterations,
             boolean premultiplyAlpha,
             Bitmap.Config outputConfig)
        performs a box blur on an image.

        The horizontal and vertical blurs can be specified separately and a number of iterations can be given which allows an approximation to Gaussian blur.

        Parameters:
        bitmap -
        hRadius - min:0 max:100
        vRadius - min:0 max:100
        iterations - the number of iterations the blur is performed. min:0 max:10. Recommended:1.
        premultiplyAlpha - whether to premultiply the alpha channel. Recommended:true
        outputConfig -
        Returns:
